/**
 * Sliding Window Rate Limiter Middleware for Express.js
 *
 * This implements a TRUE sliding window algorithm (not fixed window counters).
 *
 * IMPORTANT NOTE ON `req.ip` BEHIND PROXIES:
 * ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Express's `req.ip` (and `req.ips`) behavior depends on the 'trust proxy' setting.
 * By default, Express does NOT trust proxies, so `req.ip` will be the IP of the
 * last proxy (or the direct connection), NOT the real client IP.
 *
